Nozomi Networks Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 8:50 AM ET
Software

Company Overview of Nozomi Networks Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Nozomi Networks Inc. offers cybersecurity and operational visibility solutions for industrial control systems (ICS). The company offers SCADAguardian, a solution that provides visibility into ICS networks, devices, and process status to protect control networks from cyberattacks and operational disruptions. It serves various industries worldwide. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Menlo Park, California.


140 Scott RoadMenlo Park, CA 94025-1008United StatesFounded in 2013



nozominetworks.com







